            <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">What to Do When a Firearm Is Stolen: A Documentation Checklist</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">Nobody wants to think about it, but preparation makes all the difference. Here's exactly what to do if a firearm is stolen, and why having records matters.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span><i class="bi bi-calendar3 mr-1"></i> March 25, 2026</span>
